                  </hi>. On the 5th of June, a little before ten o'clock in the evening, I was on Ludgate-hill—I felt a tug at my coat pocket, and</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183606130050"></xptr>
               <p>turned and saw the prisoner drop my handkerchief from his hand—I gave him in charge directly—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> You was it on the ground? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I saw you drop it—there were two of you, one ran away.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
