                  </hi>. I was walking with Mr. Stevens, he turned round—I turned and saw the prisoner drop the handkerchief, the other man ran off, and I pursued, but he got away.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I saw the two gentlemen walking, and a young man behind them—they turned and the handkerchief laid on the ground—the man that took it ran away—they charged me with stealing it.</p>
